{"id":27492,"date":"2019-04-10T21:36:44","date_gmt":"2019-04-10T17:36:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=27492"},"modified":"2021-11-07T10:42:06","modified_gmt":"2021-11-07T06:42:06","slug":"whoever-worships-muhammad","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/10\/whoever-worships-muhammad\/","title":{"rendered":"Abu Bakr on Muhammad: Whoever worships the Prophet, he has died"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Ibn Abbas reported: Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, went to the door of the mosque when he heard the news of the passing of the Prophet. Abu Bakr said, \u201cTo proceed: Whoever among you worships Muhammad, peace and blessings be upon him, then Muhammad has died. Whoever worships Allah, then Allah is alive and cannot die. Allah Almighty said: <strong>Muhammad is not but a Messenger. Messengers have passed before him. If he dies or is killed, will you turn back on your heels?<\/strong>\u201d (3:144) Ibn Abbas said, \u201cBy Allah, it was as if the people had not known that Allah revealed this verse until Abu Bakr recited it.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1241<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u064f\u0648 \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u062d\u064e\u062a\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0628\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u062c\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u062d\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0644\u064e\u063a\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0629 \u062